Enjoyment
================================
If life is a rotating electron then enjoyment is the proton/neutron which is located at center of nucleus..
Ie. Enjoyment is the center of life for healthy movement.
Within the life enjoyment is the most valuable moment but beyond the life there is no meaning of enjoyment.
In other words there is no any enjoyment beyond the life.

Beyond the life
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Beyond the life when observation enter inside the streaming of object, in fact when it enter inside the present/instant moment
in deeper mode, a life forget that it is a life and in other words when the feeling enjoyment truncate itself.The frequency of heat is unable to receive any frequency and the streaming in brain(FOE) is in very light mode just like slow floating of flower in stream of river. 
Ex- 
-Deep meditation
-Extreme state of dancing in alone with closed eye.
-Extreme state of observation proceed to during deep observation
-Very light observation of self
-Very Light Flow with climate/environment
..so on..

Withing the life
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Life start with moment, Within life every one need enjoyment any ways.
Withing life Enjoyment is the necessary feeling, without enjoyment life become the 
bored/hopeless/struggling/tense/worry/dry/thirsty..so..on.
Every moment cross the life with/without enjoyment.

With enjoyment
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Enjoyment moment can be automated or one we create.
ie Enjoyment is under some expectation or free from the expectation

Self enjoyment/Nil expectation(delight)
----------------------------------------
One should know every instance/object have its own frequency and when it interact with similar frequency's object of same amplitude the frequency of object become large(max double) or enhance the frequency of object.

When one activate their self energy in such a sate that its frequency match with most of the object/stuff crossing with 
them self. Because of the matching of frequency the frequency an amplitude of both object increase.
So one feel inner healing/very good.
Without any work done by one, it feel healing.
It is just like when a normal human enter to some adventures  place/natural place/greenery/look many beautiful girls together/look the birds flying in sky in random motion/..so on, they get the good feeling.

The above situation make good feel of normal humans since it enhance their frequency of feeling..
But for the human/lives whose energy is in active state, their frequencies can match with every situation mostly from where they cross and so they feel inner healing and hence enjoyment.

This is not costless but the workdone for this enjoyment is so long in single unique direction for making the energy in active state

ex-(many year of work done happen for activation of energy) 
-meditation
-yoga
-silence
-deep analyses 
-detection of own frequencies
