The moment on feel tense, hopeless,struggle,worry...so on.
This is because of lack of energy. The power of observation is very low.This situation arise when one think too much in a fear/hindrance state of mind.
A mind is in fear/hindrance state...one can observe what it can be able to think to come out from some critical situation.
How much it will think..it will lead the hindrance only more and more.

***One should keep their battery charged every moment***

